_header: A priest sometime was in Rome me cleped Saturnine
_description: Life of St Saturninus, in one MS of the South English Legendary — in couplets

Bod779.First Lines:
A prest somtyme was in rome me cleped saturnyneþat hadde wit
                    him a dekene þat was I hote cysine…
Bod779.Last Lines:
…Now Ihesu crist al myȝty god for here boþer
                    louebring vs to þe blisse þat is in heuen aboue
Bod779.Attributed Title: Seint saturnin and cicin twey holy marteres (f. 235v)
